<p><strong>What does exclusive mean?</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Our exclusive hotels offer a relaxed atmosphere with the private feel of a chalet. Facilities that you would expect to find in a hotel, such as spa areas and a private bar. They are managed or run by Inghams Staff (or in some cases a 3rd party local team).</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>What catering is included with exclusive?</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>You'll enjoy 6 nights of catering with breakfast, afternoon tea and dinner.</li>
<li>Dinner begins with a prosecco apéritif with canapés and will then move onto a 3 or 4 course dinner/buffet, dependent on the hotel you choose to stay in.</li>
<li>Your meal is accompanied by a selection of red, white and rose wine, ending with tea or coffee.</li>
</ul>
